  "body": "<div align=\"center\">\n  <h1>Simple Saddle</h1>\n  <br/>\n  <p>\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Release-1.1.0-limegreen\" alt=\"Release\">\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Minecraft-1.16.x%201.21.5_+_25w19a-blue?logo=data:image/png;base64,&logoWidth=50\" alt=\"Minecraft\">\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/License-CC_BY_4.0-blueviolet\" alt=\"License CC BY 4.0\">\n    <a href=\"https://discord.gg/Tq83Zuhduv\" target=\"_blank\">\n      <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/1358706268012810350?color=5865F2&label=Discord&logo=discord&logoColor=white\" alt=\"Discord\">\n    </a>\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/modrinth/dt/eZ3jWMtL?logo=modrinth&label=Modrinth\" alt=\"Modrinth\">\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<br/>\n<br/>\n\n<h2>✨ Features</h2>\n<h3>🧪 Main description</h3>\n<blockquote>This datapack allows players to craft saddles using accessible and logical materials, removing the dependency on dungeon loot, fishing, or villagers.<br/> It’s perfect for early-game riders or players who don’t want to rely on RNG to explore on horseback.</blockquote>\n\n<br/>\n\n<h2>🧪 Recipes</h2>\n<blockquote>\n  <img src=\"https://nat688.github.io/AllPlugs-datapacks/images/simple-x/simple-saddle.png\" alt=\"Saddle Craft\">\n</blockquote>\n\n<br/>\n\n<h2>📥 Installation</h2>\n<h3>📁 Datapack</h3>\n<blockquote>\n  Drop the <code>.zip</code> file into your world's <code>datapacks</code> folder.<br/>\n  Reload the world or use <code>/reload</code>.<br/>\n  Enjoy your enchanted adventure!\n</blockquote>\n\n<h3>⚙️ Mod</h3>\n<blockquote>\n  Drop the <code>.jar</code> file into the <code>mods</code> folder of your instance.<br/>\n  <code>Restart</code> your game.<br/>\n  Have fun!\n</blockquote>",
